      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 43.1 - 老子 43.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 43.1 - 老子 43.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>天下之至柔，馳騁天下之至堅。無有入無間，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The softest thing in the world dashes against and overcomes the hardest; that which has no (substantial) existence enters where there is no crevice.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
